## Demo plugin

This is a demo plugin for my OctoberCMS CRUD article for Sitepoint.

You can use the `UniqueValue` form widget like the following:

```yaml
// fields.yaml

fields:
    slug:
        label: Slug
        type: \Rafie\SitepointDemo\FormWidgets\UniqueValue
        modelClass: \RainLab\Blog\Models\Post
        selectFrom: slug
        pattern: text
```